   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Has brought Palemon son of Ptollas, (for) the 4th epigraphe, of the village of the horiodeiktia of Karanis, one-hundred and fifty litrai of chaff. I, Philippos, have signed. In the 18th and 17th and 10th year, on Tybi [- -].</ab>
